[30;1m129 | [0m[35m~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~[0m
[30;1m130 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m131 | [0m[35mSometimes data sections have comment line inside them. By default lasio will ignore[0m
[30;1m132 | [0m[35many lines starting with the "#" character within the data section. You can[0m
[30;1m133 | [0m[35mcontrol this using the ``remove_data_line_filter='#'`` argument to[0m
